# Composition Guide

**Figma:** [Composition](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=83-32628&p=f&m=dev) | [Chat interface](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=4309-529&p=f&m=dev)

Layout patterns, nav bar, footer, hero, cards, forms, dashboard, sidebar, and chat interface below are derived from Figma nodes 83:32628 and 4309:529.

---

