## Navigation bar

- **Height:** ~64px; Space/800 padding.
- **Layout:** Logo left; nav items center/right; search + CTA right.
- **Background:** `--bg-base-default` or `--bg-base-secondary`.
- **Items:** Space/400–600 gap; active `--text-brand-default`.
- **Search:** Compact input; CTA: primary button.

---

## Footer

- **Layout:** Two-column; branding + links.
- **Left:** Logo + social icons; **Right:** Link columns (4 cols).
- **Gap:** Space/600–1200 between columns.
- **Links:** `--text-base-secondary`; hover `--text-brand-default`.

---

## Hero / content block

- Centered title + subtitle.
- Large padding: Space/1200–1600.
- Background: `--bg-base-secondary` or `--bg-base-default`.

---

## Questionnaire / rating form

- Section: Heading + description.
- Radio groups: Yes/No per question.
- Vertical rhythm: Space/400–600 between sections; Space/200–300 within groups.

---

## Cards

| Type | Structure |
|------|-----------|
| Product | Image placeholder; title; description; CTA button |
| Pricing | Prominent price; supporting text |
| Testimonial | Quote; author; title; optional Edit button |

**Spacing:** Space/200–400 internal padding; Space/400–600 card gap.

---

## Image gallery

- Thumbnails: row of small squares.
- Main: larger placeholder to the right or below.
- Gap: Space/200–400.

---

## Alerts

| Type | Container | Icon | Button |
|------|-----------|------|--------|
| Success | `--bg-success-tertiary` | `--text-success-default` | `--bg-success-default` |
| Error | `--bg-danger-tertiary` | `--text-danger-default` | `--bg-danger-default` |
| Warning | `--bg-warning-tertiary` | `--text-warning-default` | `--bg-warning-default` |

---

## Form composition (multi-field)

- Title: "Shipping Details" or equivalent.
- Two-column layout when space allows.
- Fields: Full Name, Email, Phone, Address, City, State, Zip, Country.
- Checkbox: "Remember me" or similar.
- Actions: Cancel (secondary) + Save (primary).
- Spacing: Space/300–400 between rows; Space/400 between sections.

---

## Dashboard / data list

- **Top bar:** Search input; "Add New" (primary); Sort dropdown; Filter dropdown; View toggle.
- **Table:** Columns NAME, STATUS, DATE, TYPE, ACTIONS.
- **Rows:** Checkbox; data; ellipsis (actions).
- **Sidebar:** Collapsible sections (Rules, User, Settings).
- **Background:** `--bg-base-secondary`; surface `--bg-base-default`; borders `--border-base-default`.

---

## Sidebar navigation

- Vertical collapsible sections.
- Hierarchy: section header; sub-items with optional counts.
- Active: `--bg-brand-tertiary`.
- Width: ~240–280px; Space/200–300 padding.

---

## Chat / Conversation interface

- **Layout:** Three-pane: left sidebar (chat history); main chat area; optional right pane or inline input.
- **Left sidebar:** Header (title + hamburger + search); Search input; Chat list (scrollable). Selected: `--bg-brand-tertiary`. User profile at bottom.
- **Main area:** User messages (right); AI messages (left); code blocks (monospace, `--bg-base-tertiary`, Radius/100, Space/200 padding).
- **Input:** Text area "What would you like to know?"; placeholder `--text-disabled-default`. Icons: layout/grid, code `</>`, microphone. Send: `--bg-brand-default` when active; `--border-base-default` when disabled.
- **Spacing:** Message gaps Space/400–600; input padding Space/200–300.
- **Sidebar width:** ~240–320px.

---

